{"word":"ροιζέω","slug":"ροιζέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ροιζέω</b></el> <el>(ροιζέω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ροῖζος'><el>ροῖζος</el></a>\n<p/><i>to whistle</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>stridere</el>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; of a snake, <i>to hiss</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to rush through</i> the <i>air</i>, <el>ἐρροίζητο</el> (3rd sg. plup.) <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/>"}]}